&lt;p&gt;Also, I have noticed that &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-18228&quot; title=&quot;Reorganize Apache C* docs in trunk branch to match the IA&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-18228&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-18228&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; moved the sections &lt;tt&gt;cql&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;data-modeling&lt;/tt&gt; into a new &lt;tt&gt;developing&lt;/tt&gt; section. However, all the links to the pages in those sections haven&apos;t been updated. The &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/2609/commits/6272442fed00d8a4aa8751e87e646148286e3fab&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;second commit&lt;/a&gt; of the PR tries to fix this.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CC &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=polandll&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;polandll&quot;&gt;polandll&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=mck&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;mck&quot;&gt;mck&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=smiklosovic&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;smiklosovic&quot;&gt;smiklosovic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
